The Seretean Wellness Center will have a onehour seminar called  at noon today as part of the centers  series PERIOD



Kenda Baker a physician assistant at the center will talk about treatment for skin damage resulting from sun exposure PERIOD Baker said she will also be addressing the skin issues that arise from old age and the cosmetic touchups that can be done to mask blemishes and wrinkles PERIOD



 said Baker PERIOD



Samantha Harp front desk receptionist at the Wellness Center said  people are expected to attend the event PERIOD



The Wellness Center is between the newly remodeled Colvin Center and the intramural fields on Hall of Fame Avenue PERIOD
